  "text": "Knikker et al. [CITATION_1] found by experiment that η i scales with the Zel'dovich flame thickness δ z = α T0 /S L . A recent DNS analysis [CITATION_2] found that η i does indeed scale with L G and η OC for the CF and TRZ regimes, respectively, but also scales with δ z for both regimes.",
